wikipedia25.cta-text: Tita taa wanto-wanto'a to delomo bali lo dunia?
wikipedia25.cta-description: Tamani spesial wola-wolata olemo to delomo bali lo dunia lonto putu lo puzzle. Lolohe tiyo wawu wolo habari u wola-wolato to dulahu pilotutuwa o-25 lo taawunu Wikipedia.
